</div></div></section><section id="ref-list1" class="ref-list"><h2 class="pmc_sec_title">References</h2>
<section id="ref-list1_sec2"><ul class="ref-list font-sm" style="list-style-type:none">
<li id="b1-0529_amia_2011_proc">
<span class="label">1.</span><cite>UMLS – Metathesaurus    <a href="http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/knowledge_sources/metathesaurus/index.html" class="usa-link" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">http://www.nlm.nih.gov/research/umls/knowledge_sources/metathesaurus/index.html</a>. Accessed: March 16, 2011.</cite>
